Subject Language(s): English (eng)

Call Deadline: 01-Mar-2007 

Meeting Description:
The English Linguistics Panel of the Rocky Mountain MLA invites the submission
of papers/presentations for its session at the 61st annual convention, held this
year in Calgary, Alberta, Canada on October 4-6, 2007. Submissions in any area
of English linguistics or related fields are welcome; graduate students are
encouraged to submit. 

Submission Requirements: 300-word abstract.
Submissions must be received by March 1, 2007.

Send electronic submissions as a Word attachment to: 
rcote@email.arizona.edu

Address print submissions to:
Robert Cote
Center for English as a Second Language
Bldg 24
P.O. Box 210024
Tucson, AZ 85721-0024

Panelists will be notified by March 15, 2007 and must secure or renew RMMLA
membership by April 1, 2007. For more information, please see the RMMLA website,
http://rmmla.wsu.edu/ or email Robert Cote, Panel Chair, at rcote@email.arizona.edu






 



